title: Ep108: 31 Year Old Virgin Feat Akaash Singh
itunes:title: Ep108: 31 Year Old Virgin Feat Akaash Singh
description:
Akaash and his lovely girlfriend join Weezy in the studio for an amazing conversation regarding why he held out his virginity for the perfect woman. Jasleen comes in and shares her sexual experiences, their first time, and how indian culture influenced some of their decision making. One of the few couples we have had on this show, this was quite interesting! Follow @Akaashsing on twitter and IG and listen to his hilarious podcast Flagrant 2

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
